Brown sausage in large skillet on medium-high heat 5 min.; drain. Stir in tomatoes with their liquid, the water and seasoning. Bring to boil. Add Shells. Reduce heat to medium-low; cover. Simmer 7 min., stirring every 3 min. Add broccoli; cook an additional 5 min. or until tender. Stir in Cheese Sauce until well blended.